Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.CLI

Class ClientPersonality

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.client.CLI.ClientPersonality
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ClientPersonality extends Object implements Serializable
Class ClientPersonality holds basic information about a Personality state in order to render its content through CLI and GUI interfaces. It carries information about its cost, whether it has been used or not and whether it's active or not. Student tiles are memorised for Lobby personality student tiles, ban counts for Ban Personality.
